// ============================================================================
// FAMILY — integration awareness (what does the agent actually CALL?)
// ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
// These are recall questions about the app's own integration surface —
// "what tool sends my texts?", "can you talk to telegram?". Auto-
// generated rows from the integrations bucket cover the obvious shape
// ("What does the agent use Gmail for?"); the rows below capture the
